{"tid":2433934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"68歲陳友接種中國科興疫苗　高舉V字手勢：大家唔怕打","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T00:58:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c25bd98912f80757504521021a618c5806d5e61f","tid":2433934,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫苗接種計劃全面展開，雖然近日有市民接種中國科興疫苗後感不適、甚至出現死亡個案，不過仍無損部分市民的信心。樂隊溫拿鼓手、現年68歲的陳友亦在內地社交平台上載接種科興疫苗時的短片，他寫着：「我打疫苗了，中國科興疫苗」。<br />\n<br />\n片中，陳友一邊接種疫苗一邊說：「多啲人打好嘅，唔係好覺痛，打完喇已經，所以大家唔怕打。」隨後更笑得非常開心兼高舉V字手勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210305/444511839632494592163509.jpeg/P1EG2K8RW6xbuWwhguTjxRi9J0zGlJsRJ3h7_yd4e_8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210305%2F444511839632494592163509.jpeg%2FP1EG2K8RW6xbuWwhguTjxRi9J0zGlJsRJ3h7_yd4e_8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=34061315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210305/444511928556589056871953.jpeg/Ko-szfHm8kpDhwQEbVKIiwMGmQqgjN0SyKLzjcii840?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210305%2F444511928556589056871953.jpeg%2FKo-szfHm8kpDhwQEbVKIiwMGmQqgjN0SyKLzjcii840%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0e15e125&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ad9dee4852024387e247a58a11a255d1bfc396c","tid":2433934,"uid":64073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"gchi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec69c16a762b34071e96e7d01fdfdfe25b48733","tid":2433934,"uid":127575,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvT5ahd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvT5ahd.gif&h=0ee74693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b71542d0bdb1466311b55157a20ca9e17758ef","tid":2433934,"uid":353587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score